<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><copyright>1977</copyright>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā waḥīda ạlậbi ḥaqaⁿ̃ạ
 ạản̊ta jī̊̉ta min̊ ʿulạk̊
 wāảẓ̊har̊ta lanā ḥubaⁿ̃ạ
 lam̊ yukẖ̊bir̊ bihi siwāk̊

[V2]
 2- ạản̊ta juz̊ta ạl̊maẘta waḥ̊dak̊
 lanā ạảk̊mal̊ta ạl̊wuʿūd̊
 wāảẓ̊har̊ta lanā maj̊dak̊
 fī ạl̊qīāmi wālṣũʿūd̊

[V3]
 3- sẖaẘkaẗa ạl̊maẘti kasar̊ta
 mun̊hīaⁿạ haẘla ạlrãday̱
 wāldãẙnūnaẗa ạḥ̊tamal̊ta
 ẓāfiraⁿạ ʿalay̱ ạl̊ʿiday̱

[V4]
 4- fī ạlsãmāʾi qad̊ dakẖal̊ta
 sābiqaⁿạ lil̊mū̊̉minīn̊
 fī ạlạảʿālī qad̊ jalas̊ta
 sayĩdaⁿạ lil̊ʿālamīn̊

[V5]
 5- wasatā̊̉tīnā sarīʿaⁿạ
 lạikẖ̊tiṭāfi ạl̊qidĩysīn̊
 wasanaf̊raḥu jamīʿaⁿạ
 ạảyũhā ạl̊fādī ạlạảmīn̊</lyrics>
<title>yạ wḥyd ạlậb ḥqạ</title>
</song>